Sharpen your taste buds and come hungry, because we'd like your expert opinion as we put readymade supermarket items to a strenuous taste test. It's a feast, it's fun and it's FREE.All tasters will go home with a copy of the latest Sunday Times Cookbook as a thank you.When: Saturday, March 11, from 10am to 1pm.How to sign up: e-mail your contact details to moorep@timesmedia.co.za by Tuesday, March 7 2017, and we will confirm your attendance. Places are limited.